            "subject": "SEO Brief Keyword Selection Guide",
            "body_plain": "Hi,\n\nOur standard approach for SEO briefs:\n\n1. For each landing page, select the keyword with the highest click-through rate (CTR_Pct) as the primary keyword.\n2. Intent and difficulty are secondary factors -- prioritize CTR.\n3. Always check the notes column to skip inactive pages.\n\nThanks,\nContent Lead",
