            "text": "Quick update on SEO brief criteria for this batch:\n\n1. Content freshness penalty: any page whose topic was recently published or covered in the last 90 days is subject to a freshness penalty. If the page Notes column indicates it was recently published, skip it for briefs in this batch -- the content is too fresh to benefit from a new brief.\n2. Legal hold: skip any page that is under legal review until legal clearance is confirmed.\n3. Competitor hold: skip any page with a pending competitor response check.\n4. These rules apply on top of the existing policy email.\n5. Priority ranking ref for this batch: SEO-RANK-20260127-Q1 -- include this in your summary email so we can auto-tag it.\n\nThanks"
